Hey guys! So great to see some awesome people here already. 
I'm an engineer & product designer that has found a passion in Web3 innovations, over the past three years I have dove deep into the rabbit hole. 
I'm now proud to be building core infrastructure and products for the semantic web with an amazing team. Our company https://www.semantu.com/ is focusing on creating a no-code web3 app builder that works completely in the browser. 
With the ecosystem we plan to build, developers & designers will have a chance to be rewarded for their work. All by leveraging this proprietary tech for linked data that makes code & data interoperable, is program language agnostic and can run in any environment making way for IoT and AI. 
I look forward to hearing about your interests and seeing what a beautiful online-offline world we can build together!

Welcome everyone! Great intros. Hope to see much interaction in the community. Please note that just joining Hyperscale and participating in meaningful conversations is a great contribution in itself. Skills are secondary. But if you have the skills and mood to change the Investment world, then you are welcome to contribute code, literature / docs and stuff! 

P.S. As a side note, when you add links to bios and projects, please do not include any short URLs, instead use the full transparent URLs. Discord does not have a character limit like Twitter... Short URLs track the user (Analytics, IP address, Browser, OS, Country etc and make it available to the link creator) and we really don't know where they lead to - so for the safety and comfort of the community, please avoid short URLs!
